  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK351">
<l>poruḷalla vaṟṟaip poruḷeṉ ṟuṇaru</l>
<l>maruḷāṉā māṇāp piṟappu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Inglorious births are produced by the confusion (of mind) which considers those things to be real which are not real.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
